&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;apos;MS Mincho&amp;apos;; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal"&gt;事業内容&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="border-left: 1px none #000000; border-top: 1px none #000000; border-right: 1px none #000000; border-bottom: 1px none #000000; vertical-align: middle"&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;apos;MS Mincho&amp;apos;; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal"&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px"&gt;菓子、食品、冷菓、牛乳・乳製品の製造及び販売&lt;/span&gt;
